---
title: Smart BBQ-Spiced Chicken with Warm Potato Salad and Green Onion Sour Cream
description: A warm dill pickle potato salad with green beans and juicy, BBQ-seasoned chicken tenders will have you channeling summer vibes at your dinner table tonight!

